Disease Resistant					KEY:Flying Fox ~ Disease Resistant			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FlyingFoxRacialTrait											DESC:Flying foxes are resistant to disease. They receive a +4 racial bonus on saving throws against disease.																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.112	ASPECT:SaveBonus|+4 on saves vs. disease

#Penguin
Toboggan						KEY:Penguin ~ Toboggan					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.PenguinRacialTrait												DESC:On snow- or ice-covered terrain, a penguin can move at a rate of 30 feet by sliding on its belly rather than walking.																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.112

#Trilobite
Curl							KEY:Trilobite ~ Curl					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.TrilobiteRacialTrait											DESC:As a standard action, a trilobite can curl into a ball, increasing its natural armor bonus by 2 but preventing it from taking any move actions. Uncurling is a standard action.																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.113
